AWS EC2 RightSizing — Consumption Analysis & SKU Recommendations
Description

Analyze actual EC2 utilization across AWS accounts and recommend the most cost-effective instance SKUs to reduce cloud spend and improve efficiency.

Acceptance criteria

All EC2 instances identified across accounts/regions
Utilization metrics collected (CPU, memory, network, disk) over 14–30 days
Over-provisioned / under-utilized instances flagged
Best-fit SKU recommended per instance
Report includes current vs recommended type, cost savings & risk level
